OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FAds for supermarkets Lidl and Iceland
OL,8,Fhave become the first to be banned
OL,9,Funder new rules governing "less
OL,10,Fhealthy" food and drink.
OL,12,FThe rules are part of government
OL,13,Fefforts to tackle childhood obesity by
OL,14,Fpreventing ads for food and drink that
OL,15,Fis high in fat, salt and sugar (HFSS)
OL,16,Fappearing on television between 5.30am
OL,17,Fand 9pm, and online at any time.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FThe ban, which came into effect at the
OL,8,Fbeginning of the year, applies to
OL,9,Fproducts that fall within 13
OL,10,Fcategories considered to play the most
OL,11,Fsignificant role in childhood obesity.
OL,13,FThese include soft drinks, chocolates
OL,14,Fand sweets, pizzas and ice creams, but
OL,15,Falso breakfast cereals and porridges,
OL,16,Fsweetened bread products, and main
OL,17,Fmeals and sandwiches.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FProducts that fall into these
OL,8,Fcategories are then also assessed on
OL,9,Fwhether they are "less healthy" based
OL,10,Fon a scoring tool that considers their
OL,11,Fnutrient levels and whether products
OL,12,Fare high in saturated fat, salt or
OL,13,Fsugar.
OL,15,FOnly products that meet both criteria
OL,16,Fare included in the restrictions.
OL,18,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,19,F(ASA) said an Instagram post for Lidl
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland by influencer Emma
OL,21,FKearney
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,Ffeatured the grocer's cheese pretzel,
OL,8,Fwhich was not categorised as HFSS and
OL,9,Ftherefore did not fall within the
OL,10,Frestrictions, and its Pain Suisse
OL,11,Fproduct, which was classified as both
OL,12,FHFSS and a sweetened bread product and
OL,13,Fwas therefore banned under the new
OL,14,Frules.
OL,16,FLidl said the ad had been removed and
OL,17,Fthey had liaised with their marketing
OL,18,Fagency to ensure that all future ads
OL,19,Fcomplied with the new rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FIn a separate case, Iceland confirmed
OL,8,Fthat two ads included a tub of
OL,9,FSwizzles Sweet Treats, a packet of
OL,10,FChupa Chups Laces, a bag of Chooee
OL,11,FDisco Stix and a bag of Haribo Elf
OL,12,FSurprises, which were all classified
OL,13,Fas HFSS.
OL,15,FThey also provided nutrient profile
OL,16,Finformation from their supplier which
OL,17,Fconfirmed that Pringles Sour Cream &
OL,18,FOnion crisps, also included in the
OL,19,Fads, were not an HFSS product.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FIceland's Luxury Aberdeen Angus Beef
OL,8,FRoasting Joint, Vegetable Spring
OL,9,FRolls, Sticky Chicken Skewers and
OL,10,FLurpak Spreadable Butter, which were
OL,11,Falso included in the ads, did not fall
OL,12,Fwithin the new restrictions.
OL,14,FThe ASA did not uphold a complaint
OL,15,Fagainst an Instagram post by
OL,16,Finfluencer John Fisher ` known to many
OL,17,Fas Big John ` which featured him
OL,18,Fpromoting menu items at a new German
OL,19,FDoner Kebab outlet because the
OL,20,Fspecific items shown in the ad were
OL,21,Fnot classified as less healthy foods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FThe watchdog also cleared a TV ad for
OL,8,FOn The Beach promoting free airport
OL,9,Flounge access which featured a boy
OL,10,Fapproaching a buffet and taking a
OL,11,Fchocolate ring doughnut.
OL,13,FThe ASA said viewers would see the ad
OL,14,Fas showing an example of what was
OL,15,Favailable in the lounge rather than
OL,16,Ffor the doughnut itself, meaning it
OL,17,Fdid not break the rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
