CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FASA chief executive Guy Parker said:
OL,13,F"As the ad regulator, our role is to
OL,14,Fremain impartial and independent,
OL,15,Fmaking sure our new LHF rules, which
OL,16,Freflect the law, are applied fairly
OL,17,Fand consistently.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
