OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,F"These initial rulings are an
OL,8,Fimportant step in building a clearer
OL,9,Fpicture of how the rules are applied
OL,10,Fin reality.
OL,12,F"We'll be continuing to play our role
OL,13,Fin administering and enforcing them,
OL,14,Fincluding by using tech-assisted
OL,15,Fproactive monitoring."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
