FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776287489
OL,3,CLidl and Iceland ads are first to be
OL,4,Cbanned under new 'less healthy' food
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FAn Iceland spokesman said: "The
OL,8,Fproducts highlighted were part of a
OL,9,Fbigger range in the specific display
OL,10,Fad and were featured due to a
OL,11,Ftechnical fault with a data feed from
OL,12,Fa third-party supplier.
OL,14,F"As the ASA has pointed out, these
OL,15,Finitial rulings are helping to build a
OL,16,Fclearer picture of how the new rules
OL,17,Fare applied, following the initial
OL,18,Fconfusion and debate around the
OL,19,Fregulations."
OL,26,@oD@\OUvD@AOU{D@MO]
